# AltGen Project Rules

## Project Overview

**Description:** This is a Firefox browser extension called AltGen that generates alt text for images on WordPress sites using AI. It uses JavaScript, HTML, CSS, WebExtensions APIs, OpenAI API, and WordPress REST API.

